Happy birthday to my Julia Gulia!! Your birthday was yesterday, but I was waiting on Mom to send me some cautieee baby photos of us. A sister bond is something that no one else can replicate and you always remind me of how lucky I am to be your big sis. You are my forever best friend (sorry you’re stuck with me🤪), my blonde other half, the best secret keeper, or as some say, the more chill version of me 😂 Even though you are so far away, I could not do life without you! My Baby Julia you are so beautiful inside and out and you always know the right things to say💖I love you with all my heart and I can’t wait to be inseparable next week! 💃🏼💃🏻
